		    	<div class="content col-md-8">
		    		<h1 style="text-align: left;">Market Leaders in Narrow Web Label Slitter Rewinders, Die Cutting Rewinders, Digital Label Converting &amp; Finishing Systems, Flexible Packaging Slitting Equipment.</h1>
<p>Bar Graphic Machinery Ltd are a market leader in the design and manufacture of Label Finishing, Die Cutting Slitter Rewinders, Digital Label Converting Finishing Systems and Flexible Packaging Finishing Equipment for the Label Printing and Flexible Packaging industries worldwide.</p>
<p>We are passionate about what we do and our machines are highly regarded and proven within the industry. They have been installed in a wide range of leading Label Manufacturers and Packaging companies since our establishment in 1992, with an enviable worldwide reputation for reliability and performance. Repeat business with existing customers has enabled our company to become a chosen supplier to many leading print and flexible packaging companies.</p>
<p>In-House technical innovation has been the driving force behind our success to date with constant product development to meet the changing needs and requirements of our customers. &nbsp;We are so confident in our machinery that we offer a three year guarantee on all in-house manufactured parts, as well as outstanding after sales service and product support!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
